{"id": 3007, "genre": 1000, "title": "生活中，你觉得自己最需要哪种“一起做这件事”的同伴？", "description": "在哪些事情上，你会觉得“多个人（不一定是朋友）跟自己一起，这件事会变得更有意思”？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 6880, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190922205225JYxsElZib9o1Q6vO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-22T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5935, "title": "生活中，你觉得自己最需要哪种“一起做这件事”的同伴？", "content": "现如今，你觉得自己最需要哪种“一起做这件事”的同伴？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 347078, "content": "Snackmate，喝奶茶吃零食都能拉对方一起买", "image": "img/option/option/20190922190251xFu4BpN2fd96y71T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347079, "content": "Tripmate，共同研究攻略，出门旅行固定搭档", "image": "img/option/option/20190922190454vlzQVgipWIHGmAyZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347081, "content": "Focusmate，临时监工，一起干活并监督对方", "image": "img/option/option/20190922190609XwWkCd29qh3gKHpr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347082, "content": "Procrastimate，一起拖延划水（并互相安慰", "image": "img/option/option/20190922190915wC018OhaKLy5jSkH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347083, "content": "Gamemate，一起肝游戏，组队打怪做任务", "image": "img/option/option/20190922191307hZMq3oijEVdJN0IF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347086, "content": "Chatmate，就像树洞一样互相听对方唠家常", "image": "img/option/option/20190922191750YvQyMPp8NZE1kn6O.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347087, "content": "Shoppingmate，互甩砍价链接，一起种草凑单", "image": "img/option/option/20190922192630xXQOU5L2wjkPlpKI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347089, "content": "Catmate，互相分享猫片并一起云吸猫", "image": "img/option/option/20190922194134DhEYox4f7skM8BqT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347090, "content": "不用了，这些事我还是喜欢独自完成", "image": "img/option/option/20190922194406NxZ3DeYGnIy50mP2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}